JAMES JONES and wife, ALBERTA JONES, v. R. H. HEWITT, et al., as Trustees of Mount Olive A. M. E. Church. 20 So. (2nd) 696

January Term, 1945

February 6, 1945 Division A *536M. R. McDonald, for appellants. Joe D. Kinsey, and Howard G. Livingston, for appellees. PER CURIAM:

The record and briefs having been duly considered and no error appearing, the decree appealed from is affirmed.

CHAPMAN, C. J., TERRELL, BUFORD and ADAMS, JJ., concur.
